videos.description: Texas A&M-CC cannot locate Jordan Bowden on defense as he slashes to the rack and jams the dunk for Tennessee.
videos.headline: Bowden slams home transition dunk for Tennessee

videos.description: Admiral Schofield steals a pass and flushes the breakaway dunk to put Tennessee up 17 in the second half.
videos.headline: Schofield's sleight of hand leads to 2-handed slam
